{"tid":1312132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「三毛戰略」唔好再擺助攻藝人、記者同廣告商上檯，否則冇人會再敢出聲","createTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:25:39.000Z","uid":15696,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0e3b87536f8829b3430dbe4d2d600a422bc5b8","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"我發覺好多三毛特登開post「表揚」人，而連登仔跟風正評之後，大陸媒體、社交平台就嚟料用連登仔言論嚟批鬥。<br />\n<br />\n大家都知中共幾恐怖，希望大家體諒一吓同路人嘅，唔好吓吓開post「表揚」，例如廣告商只係「商業決定」，藝人只係抒發個人感受，記者只係工作之外個人行為。<br />\n<br />\n唔好令到好多人難做，唔係個個一係變哂保礦力，一係唔敢出聲或者做多啲。唔該曬大家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e1f8756057709aff67731bf3508188a77be27f","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:37:03.000Z","msg":"唔該大家唔好再被人利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讃人唔洗特別開幾個post讚 在心中"},{"pid":"5757f160a1d7823bab30a4bc2876e4b7cb0478e3","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb9f506839cac505cbcdabd40b91124e96e61c4e","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"thabk you!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ea585243752737624beb56e457ec108a8d85f","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"唔好再幫人推post!"},{"pid":"dcf2ac79cc528446d052d71ec38c5cc060012d57","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"thanks"},{"pid":"490d427b7af19a03dc781a5837e022eccb7c194c","tid":1312132,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2